CSS -Display property
Display have 4 important values -flex,inline,inline-block,block
these  are used to positioning elements in layouts

inline -element take only suffcient space
block -element takes a all space in a row
inline-block -have both the properties 
flex -is used in parent tag to position inner tag elements,elements in flex take all the space in a row or col (not take suffcient)
inline-flex -behave like flex but space is taken suffcient to all the elements(donot take a row space)
